1. *Obećao* je da će da me pozove kad se vrati iz putovanja. (He promised that he would call me when he returns from the trip.)

2. On mi je *obećao* da ću imati povoljnu cenu. (He promised me that I would have a favourable price.)

3. *Obećanje* je bilo da će da se javi u roku od tri dana. (The promise was that he would contact me within three days.)

4. On je *obećao* da će poslati pismo za vikend. (He promised that he would send the letter over the weekend.)

5. Oni su *obećali* da će nam pomoći u bilo kom trenutku. (They promised that they would help us at any moment.)